+> example:
+>
+> * `@import "..." a b(c)` could be parsed as either:
+>   * `MediaQuery "a", ImportFunction "b(c)"`
+>   * `MediaQuery "a b", MediaQuery "(c)"`
+> * `@import "..." a and(b)` could be parsed as either:
+>   * `MediaQuery "a", ImportFunction "and(b)"`
+>   * `MediaQuery "a and(b)"`
